Class RamDisk

java.lang.Object
  com.meetwise.fs.RamDisk
All Implemented Interfaces:
BlockDevice
public final class RamDisk
extends java.lang.Object
implements BlockDevice

A BlockDevice that lives entirely in heap memory. This is basically a RAM disk.

Author:
Matthias Treydte <waldheinz at gmail.com>
